{"tid":517693,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇d阻人收工既仆街","createTime":"2018-01-02T14:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T15:10:18.000Z","uid":58841,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa345c03e1e889270e8f34cef927d7bd2f7102f7","tid":517693,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:17:26.000Z","msg":"話說我間舖就9點半閂門既<br />\n咁就有條友8點45分入黎睇鞋<br />\n咁我同上司個陣都做緊野無去理佢<br />\n由得佢自己慢慢睇<br />\n點知到我地落哂閘熄埋music先黎話想試對鞋<br />\n然後我咪同佢講唔好意思先生 我地已經閂門 如果你想試可以聽朝再黎<br />\n之後佢就走左<br />\n<br />\n如果係你會點做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母咪阻撚住我收工躝屍趌路啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俗話有講客人係上帝 一於大家齊齊ot服務客人"},{"pid":"fbf4eafa591ab63eb6d7946ecc22b72941163d29","tid":517693,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"臨收舖一分鐘入嚟行 行足15分鐘乜都唔買走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e13bd0a4e9d0be046e752bb7730b0c169d3fbe6","tid":517693,"uid":87389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"要追數未跟埋佢囉<br />\n爆左數/趕收工/冇心情未叫佢走<br />\n其實未又係睇阿頭做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd94019cb1921de91da1cb1e75b575ed5d7116e2","tid":517693,"uid":156507,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"但都有d趕客走既sales<br />\n例如舖頭關9點半, 9點就落半閘, 熄射燈。 西面對住舖入面既客。"},{"pid":"116b66b4d522d1e9ba6d06774addcaea144ffbc7","tid":517693,"uid":38315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:26:46.000Z","msg":"正皮係比你句躝屍吉路 好撚難打"},{"pid":"dc5cd4ce2f53de2a3912f758f92673b2461cd526","tid":517693,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd94019cb1921de91da1cb1e75b575ed5d7116e2","tid":517693,"uid":156507,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:25:45.000Z",